divs: Sighting DetailsI was going through my photos and found this object in the middle picture of three shot on Auto focus in 2.3 seconds. I was shooting a helicopter and caught something very odd in the middle photo. It is metallic looking on top shaded below and is moving very fast. I have no idea of what I caught. thought you might like to see the three photos and judge for yourselves if it is or is not. It is a puzzler for sure as the object had to be moving very Fast It was My Dad and myself and we where celebrating Fathers day with a fishing trip to a high country styream on the east end of Grand Mesa.
Summary: Object on photo that was not seen
